public
VEvil.​Core.​LabelOverride

LabelOverride provide the possibility to change the name of a field displayed in the Editor's GUI Inspector only.  The label defined is displayed in the editor using the LabelOverridePropertyDrawer.

LabelOverride won't work for List{T}, Array, and structs.
